This is a project to assist with learning and long term information retention.

Further down the road the goal is integration with a database and a pattern
recognition tool, to make sense of the immense amounts of knowledge needed to
operate as a doctor on a daily basis.

First Goal: Set up a system for taking notes and automatically creating tests
and quizzes from them.
  This will involve scanning a text file for questions and answers, splitting
  them in two files and saving them.
